<script>
    if(window.location.pathname.endsWith("ForgotPassword")) {
        const urlParams = new URLSearchParams(window.location.search);
        const redirectValue = urlParams.get("redirect");
		
        var observer = new MutationObserver(function (mutationsList, observer) {
            for (var mutation of mutationsList) {
                if (mutation.type === 'childList' || mutation.type === 'attributes') {
                    if (document.querySelector('.community-text-title') && redirectValue == "expired") {
                        document.querySelector('.community-text-title').innerHTML = 'Contrase√±a expirada';
                        observer.disconnect();
                        break;
                    }
                }
            }
        });

        observer.observe(document, { childList: true, subtree: true, attributes: true });
    }
</script>
